data.description:
Cute house with fenced in yard and driveway with carport. Kitchen with cabinets for storage and breakfast nook with window view. Laundry area with glass door access to backyard, providing lots of natural light. Nice deck to enjoy the backyard view from.
Tankless water heater. 
CH,A - 2023
new mini split in office.
privacy fence - 2022

Seller will be painting the outside of property light gray.
